quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Koo, walolakhwo ulia owakhaya ebimanyisio biefu mana naboola mbu: “Toto esie nditsa okhuhebwa omwandu nende Abana?”"
  19,78,"Koo, ye yanyola amakhuwa kefisa, nohomba Owetsimbabaasi yamulaka?"
  19,79,"Shikali kario tawe. Khwitsa okhuhandika akaboolanga, ne khulamumeta muno ebise bieshinyasio."
  19,80,"Ne khulimuhelesia akaboolanga ako, ne alikhwitsila nali yenyene."
  19,81,"Ne bekholela abanyasaye baandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole amaani (oluyali)."
  19,82,"Shikali kario tawe. Balikongola okhulamwa khwabu okho, ne baliba abasuku babu."
  19,83,"Koo, shimulolangakhwo mbu efwe khwaruma amashetani khubakhayi, ababaretsangamwo amaani kokhukhola amabii?"
  19,84,"Kho olabayuyukhanila tawe. Efwe toto khubabalilanga tsinyanga tsiabu."
  19,85,"Inyanga yakhulikhung’asia abaria Nyasaye okhubayila khuwetsimbabaasi babe abacheni be."
  19,86,"Ne khulichomia ababii mumulilo kwa Jahannam, nibali nende omwalakho omunji."
  19,87,"Shibaliba nende obunyali bwokhusabila abandi eshileshelo tawe, halali balia bakhola indakano ewa Omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  19,88,"Ne baboola mbu: “Omunji wetsimbabaasi yekholela Omwana.”"
  19,89,"Toto mwarera likhuwa liokhusinya muno."
  19,90,"Likulu lili hambi muno okhwatikha, ne liloba okhwarukha, ne tsingulu okhukwa ebitonyetonye."
  19,91,"Khulwa bachikha mbu Omunji wetsimbabaasi yekholela Omwana."
  19,92,"Ne shikakhoyeshela Omunji Wetsimbabaasi okhwikholela Omwana tawe."
  19,93,"Abulaho yesiyesi khubali mwikulu nende mushialo halali alitsila Omunji wetsimbabaasi nali Omusumba."
  19,94,"Ne toto yamala okhubamanya, ne yababala obulayi muno."
  19,95,"Ne buli shiamulala alimwitsila Ye (Nyasaye) inyanga yeyindukho yenyene."